" Custom Nerdtree
""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
" Open nerdtree
map <C-n> :NERDTreeToggle<CR>
map <C-b> :NERDTreeFind<CR>
